Community leaders in Edmonton area where 2 police officers were killed say violence needs addressing
By
Phil Heidenreich
Global News
Posted March 16, 2023 8:18 pm
Updated March 16, 2023 11:39 pm
2:47
Gun violence concerns in Edmonton as 2 police officers latest victims in string of shootings
Gun violence concerns in Edmonton as 2 police officers latest victims in string of shootings
